{"analysis_markdown_path":"articles/2026/06/09/itm_99c3f17cdeb06ebd/index.md","canonical_url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.09701","category_id":"ai-safety","collected_at":"2026-06-09T08:37:13Z","content_hash":"f6340f1d6fcb4d2ab11df443a9f2bc49a975e6018e014fe5fce04ab3a6a09770","evidence":[{"label":"arXiv abstract and submission history","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.09701"},{"label":"arXiv-txt full text","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv-txt.org/pdf/2606.09701"},{"label":"PyRIT related framework","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2410.02828"},{"label":"HarmBench related benchmark","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2402.04249"},{"label":"Adaptive attacks background","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2510.09023"},{"label":"GDPO related method","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2601.05242"}],"external_id":"arXiv:2606.09701v1","fetched_at":"2026-06-09T08:37:13Z","fingerprint":"f6340f1d6fcb4d2ab11df443a9f2bc49a975e6018e014fe5fce04ab3a6a09770","id":"itm_99c3f17cdeb06ebd","item_id":"itm_99c3f17cdeb06ebd","language":"zh-CN","published_at":"2026-06-08T16:21:36Z","reading_minutes":26,"score":93,"sort_at":"2026-06-08T16:21:36Z","source_id":"arxiv-advgrpo-2606","source_name":"arXiv","source_type":"manual","summary_zh":"AdvGRPO 研究如何用 GRPO 同时训练自适应红队攻击者和安全防御者。论文回应既有攻防共训练中“GRPO 不稳定”的结论，提出 dense multi-channel rewards、GDPO 解耦归一化、single-turn 到 closed-loop multi-turn 再到 attacker/defender 交替更新的课程。攻击者侧用 attack reward、prompt reward 和 reasoning 模型的 thinking-trace reward；防御者侧用 1-A 和 benign helpfulness，避免只学拒绝。实验显示 Qwen2.5-14B multi-turn attacker 在 GPT-4.1 defender 上达到 AdvBench 90.0%、HarmBench 91.0% ASR，Qwen3.5-9B reasoning attacker 从 0.0/0.5 提到 79.1/71.0；迁移到 Phi-4-mini、Llama-3.1-8B、Gemma-2-9B 仍有 82.0% 到 88.5% HarmBench ASR。共训练 defender 在 HarmBench、WildJailbreak、DAN、WildGuardTest 上 ASR 降到 0.9、7.5、7.3、0.5，且 MMLU、TruthfulQA、ARC-C、IFBench 基本保持；局限是 WJB benign compliance 从 99.2 降到 72.8/69.6，攻击策略仍会 entropy collapse，reward 依赖 GPT-4.1 judge 和 HarmBench classifier，且文本红队 benchmark 不能直接代表工具型 Agent 的权限越界、数据泄露和真实部署风险。","tags":["ai-safety","red-teaming","grpo","post-training","harmbench","adversarial-training","llm-safety"],"title":"Learning to Attack and Defend: Adaptive Red Teaming of Language Models via GRPO","title_hash":"074d10f51825d11ff1d7566b910657cf06b623da4be3db1081b9f69a7b3e2fda","type":"paper","updated_at":"2026-06-08T16:21:36Z","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.09701"}
{"analysis_markdown_path":"articles/2026/06/09/itm_3b2465ec32468e9f/index.md","canonical_url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.09549","category_id":"llm-agent","collected_at":"2026-06-09T02:27:11Z","content_hash":"99b68daee2b2f7cde07512fcc941f6ffbc12577f3ae39b61071509cec296f553","evidence":[{"label":"arXiv abstract","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.09549"},{"label":"arXiv PDF","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2606.09549"},{"label":"AgentDojo NeurIPS page","type":"url","url":"https://proceedings.neurips.cc/paper_files/paper/2024/hash/97091a5177d8dc64b1da8bf3e1f6fb54-Abstract-Datasets_and_Benchmarks_Track.html"},{"label":"Agent Security Bench","type":"url","url":"https://luckfort.github.io/ASBench/"},{"label":"AgentLeak arXiv","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2602.11510"}],"external_id":"arXiv:2606.09549","fetched_at":"2026-06-09T02:27:11Z","fingerprint":"99b68daee2b2f7cde07512fcc941f6ffbc12577f3ae39b61071509cec296f553","id":"itm_3b2465ec32468e9f","item_id":"itm_3b2465ec32468e9f","language":"zh-CN","published_at":"2026-06-08T14:29:01Z","score":92,"sort_at":"2026-06-08T14:29:01Z","source_id":"arxiv-secureclaw-2606","source_name":"arXiv","source_type":"manual","summary_zh":"SecureClaw 针对工具型 LLM Agent 的两类安全失败：未授权外部动作和 runtime 内敏感明文暴露。论文把防线拆成 effect sink 的 PREVIEW->COMMIT 请求绑定授权，以及 read boundary 的 opaque handle confinement；在 AgentDojo、AgentLeak、ASB 上验证，SecureClaw 达到 ASB 0.00% ASR、AgentDojo 0.64% ASR、AgentLeak attacked parity lane 3.23% any leak，同时 ASB utility 为 88.90%。消融显示 handles 主要关闭 C2/C5 内部泄露，executor boundary 主要关闭外部动作；局限是 policy 允许区域内仍可能 wrong-principal/wrong-object，bounded summary 仍是显式 declassification channel，且依赖完整 sink mediation 和可信 gateway/policy/executor。","tags":["llm-agent","ai-safety","prompt-injection","agent-security","information-flow","tool-use"],"title":"SecureClaw: Clawing Back Control of LLM Agents","title_hash":"5b9a23bbb721c8182bb7f9591c66824d24940423160a9624e0a1a7a8589ca2ff","type":"paper","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.09549"}
{"analysis_markdown_path":"articles/2026/06/09/itm_745fe3938cac2458/index.md","canonical_url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.09447","category_id":"llm-agent","collected_at":"2026-06-09T02:35:00Z","content_hash":"0bbc71c0d08034ed6abba8eef3d7d2188da5518df7b103d9a4cd2a473a30df23","evidence":[{"label":"arXiv abstract and submission history","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.09447"},{"label":"AliyunConsoleAgent PDF","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2606.09447"},{"label":"WebAgent-R1 related paper","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2505.16421"},{"label":"ZeroGUI related paper","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2505.23762"},{"label":"CUARewardBench related paper","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2510.18596"}],"external_id":"arxiv:2606.09447v1","fetched_at":"2026-06-09T02:35:00Z","fingerprint":"0bbc71c0d08034ed6abba8eef3d7d2188da5518df7b103d9a4cd2a473a30df23","id":"itm_745fe3938cac2458","item_id":"itm_745fe3938cac2458","language":"zh-CN","published_at":"2026-06-08T12:55:42Z","score":92,"sort_at":"2026-06-08T12:55:42Z","source_id":"arxiv","source_name":"arXiv","source_type":"manual","summary_zh":"AliyunConsoleAgent 将云控制台文档校验定义为真实环境 Web Agent 任务：先用 frontier model 成功轨迹蒸馏做 SFT，再在真实 Alibaba Cloud 控制台里用 GRPO、ActionTrail 规则 reward 和双 LLM judge 训练。论文构建账号池、Kubernetes 沙箱、Resource META Terraform 预置与 ResourceCoder 运行时补资源，隔离资源缺失造成的 reward 噪声。在 278 个真实文档任务上，32B SFT+GRPO 达到 63.52% pass@1，比 base 高 20.24pp，与 Gemini 3 Pro Preview 65.34% 只差 1.82pp，且单任务成本约 0.56 CNY，较 Gemini 约低 92%。局限是 Terraform 模板维护、复杂前端非确定性、真实资源成本和仍未解决的 Agent 决策错误。","tags":["llm-agent","web-agent","reinforcement-learning","post-training","cloud-console","documentation-verification"],"title":"AliyunConsoleAgent: Training Web Agents in Real-World Cloud Environments via Distillation and Reinforcement Learning","title_hash":"d4d109020cc60442212d171ddd7236d43674f8791af2bc726cdcbc1152d8a2f7","type":"paper","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.09447"}
{"analysis_markdown_path":"articles/2026/06/04/itm_f8aa6102b06db6f8/index.md","canonical_url":"https://huggingface.co/blog/nvidia/nemotron-3-5-content-safety","category_id":"ai-safety","collected_at":"2026-06-09T08:27:03Z","content_hash":"841c7c1e9b24cec63f9b6aaf0e4477fa3e38db21ae01ab6ecf026eb150cdb87e","evidence":[{"label":"Hugging Face NVIDIA announcement","type":"url","url":"https://huggingface.co/blog/nvidia/nemotron-3-5-content-safety"},{"label":"Nemotron 3.5 Content Safety model card","type":"url","url":"https://huggingface.co/nvidia/Nemotron-3.5-Content-Safety"},{"label":"Nemotron 3.5 Content Safety dataset card","type":"url","url":"https://huggingface.co/datasets/nvidia/Nemotron-3.5-Content-Safety-Dataset"},{"label":"Nemotron 3.5 usage cookbook","type":"url","url":"https://github.com/NVIDIA-NeMo/Nemotron/tree/main/usage-cookbook/Nemotron-3.5-Content-Safety"},{"label":"Nemotron policy generator skill","type":"url","url":"https://github.com/NVIDIA-NeMo/Nemotron/tree/main/skills/nemotron-policy-generator"},{"label":"Production AI Institute independent brief","type":"url","url":"https://www.productionai.institute/insights/nvidia-nemotron-3-5-content-safety-production-impact-2026"}],"external_id":"hf-blog:nemotron-3-5-content-safety","fetched_at":"2026-06-09T08:27:03Z","fingerprint":"841c7c1e9b24cec63f9b6aaf0e4477fa3e38db21ae01ab6ecf026eb150cdb87e","id":"itm_f8aa6102b06db6f8","item_id":"itm_f8aa6102b06db6f8","language":"zh-CN","published_at":"2026-06-04T00:00:00Z","reading_minutes":22,"score":92,"sort_at":"2026-06-04T00:00:00Z","source_id":"hf-nvidia-safety-blog","source_name":"Hugging Face Blog: NVIDIA","source_type":"manual","summary_zh":"NVIDIA 在 2026-06-04 发布 Nemotron 3.5 Content Safety，把用户 prompt、可选图片、可选助手回复和企业自定义 policy 合并到一次 4B guard model 推理中；模型基于 Gemma-3-4B-it，经 LoRA 在多模态、多语言和推理型安全数据上微调，支持 Transformers、vLLM、SGLang 与 NVIDIA NIM。官方证据显示模型在多语言/多模态 harmful-content classification 评测上约 85% 平均准确率，Multilingual Aegis 约 96.5%，RTP-LX 约 88.8%，并宣称相对另一多模态安全模型端到端延迟低 3x；公开数据集约 98,316 行，含约 70k text-only 与 28k image-referenced 样本。局限是多张图表为 internally evaluated，THINK mode 会增加延迟，推理痕迹不是合规证明本身，企业仍需自建 policy 版本管理、黄金集、阈值、人工复核和 incident response。","tags":["nemotron","content-safety","multimodal-safety","guard-model","custom-policy","reasoning-trace","aegis","nvidia"],"title":"Nemotron 3.5 Content Safety: Customizable Multimodal Safety for Global Enterprise AI","title_hash":"87384bc5a3100f8dee5ed766c6adc67358c68d8c64359afa1b876952a7c759ec","type":"blog","updated_at":"2026-06-04T00:00:00Z","url":"https://huggingface.co/blog/nvidia/nemotron-3-5-content-safety"}
